title: O'NEILL WETSUITS PSYCHO RG8
description: O'Neill's EXCLUSIVE environmentally friendly UltraFlex RG8 Neoprene. For Fall 2011 we have redesigned the F.U.Z.E Closure System to make it even easier to get in and out of. We have also included RG8-Air Firewall to the chest, Super Seal cuffs, Single Fluid Seam Weld, Double Super Seal Neck, and Krypto Knee Padz. To top off this list of upgrades, the RG8 is available with a built-in hood.
